description:
Vendetta is currently ranked 3rd, with 12 full submissions. A strong wrestler with great leg skills. Vendetta is 4-0 this season and has suffered ZERO shame points. Vendetta has won all matches this season with an average score of 206 points, over her opponents.
Isis is currently ranked 4th (tied with Dragon) and has 26 full submissions to her name. Fast and competent The Goddess only has one lost this season and that lose was to Syd. The Goddess uses her speed to overcome her opponents. And there it is…
title: Vendetta (4-2)
